I am Andrea Carr who is a 41 year old wife and mom 
of 1 daughter. I am sorry I have not written before but I have a terrible year 
and haven&#39;t had the time to concentrate on EVP like I had prior. I won&#39;t get 
into the details but it has left me in the midst of OK just trying to pull 
through all of this BS & I will get back to it when I can.

Unfortunatley I am leaving for the weekend tomorrow 
morning and won&#39;t see my e-mails until Monday morning. 

I have a question for any one here. I believe in 
aliens, spirit and ghost communications via evp but tonight I had an experience 
I never had before.

I woke up at exactly 2:22 by my stove&#39;s clock and 
went and cleaned my sink of dishes while I heated up some cream chipped beef 
(albiet not too exciting) but while I sat there after in the dark with my family 
sleeping my hallway ilummating a light clored blue several times. Anyone else 
ever seen this?

I look forward to any responses.

Thanks!
Andrea 



      
